title: Facebook has launched a meme-making app called Whale
text:
Whale is just another example of Facebook wanting to have a hand in the creation of any type of content you post on its platforms.
Facebook has quietly launched a new app called Whale that allows users to quickly make memes and share them on social media, reports The Information  (via The Verge ).
